    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2020-10-20</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2021-01-21T21:27:28Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Jamal Khashoggi Press Freedom Accountability Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill establishes measures to protect the human rights of journalists.</p> <p>Specifically, the bill (1) expands the scope of required reports related to violations of the human rights of journalists, (2) requires the President to impose certain property- and visa-blocking sanctions on persons responsible for gross violations of the human rights of journalists, and (3) prohibits certain foreign assistance to a governmental entity of a country if an official acting under authority of the entity has committed a gross violation of human rights against a journalist.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
